@node "1" " Introduction "
 What is ListIt?
 ---------------
  ListIt is a utility which creates alternative File Lists, When used with
included program  @{"DIZLIST" link "16" 0} , it will create lists such as the type used with
"Elite" type Bullitin Board Systems.

  Features include:


a.  The ability to create lists for all file areas.

b.  The ability to create colorized lists (GR1-9).

c.  Automatically creates any files (not included in the archive) which it
    needs for operation.

d.  Keeps track of what file areas have changed since last execution, so it
    doesn't have to do file areas that are unchanged.

e.  Creates filelists which include long and short descriptions.
@endnode

