 Required Files
 --------------

 All the files included in the archive are required.  If you are installing
this version as an UPGRADE, click this button @{"UPDATE INFO" link "14" 0} now, then return
here.

Be sure to @{"configure" link "3" 0} the door to customize the setup for your BBS.
@endnode

