or

Keith Townsend Ami-Madness!! Eglin AFB FL 904-243-4996 24h 28000 baud Modem
Fido: 1:366/1968.0 MaxNet: 90:130/1.0

All Contacts can be made via MEBBS, MEBBS_TESTER, MEBBSNET_DEV echos (Mebbsnet
support echos). 

Preferable echo is MEBBS or netmail.

If you log on to Kitt's Korner, and choose the LEAVE FEEDBACK option, you can
choose to leave feedback either to the sysop (Keith) or to Larry. Please
ensure you leave messages FOR Larry TO Larry.

On Keith's board, leave feedback to PHANTOM.

PLEASE ensure that you give the version number of the ListIt you are using.  I
try to keep a copy of one version back.  If you haven't got the latest
version, get it from any @{"CSR Site" link "12" 0}, because I may have already fixed that bug
you were going to report!
