@node "13" "Installing / Running Arexx"
 Installing Arexx
 ----------------

This door REQUIRES the use of AmigaDos 2.04 or higher.  Since thats the case,
AREXX should already be installed and running in our system, unless you
specifically took it out of your startup scripts.  If thats the case, see your
AMIGADOS manual for instructions on re-installing AREXX on your system.  This
door will NOT work without the AREXX server being active.
@endnode

