@node "15" "Future info"
 What does the future hold for ListIT?
 -------------------------------------

We we were hoping that some enterprising programmer would write a door that
would display TXT or GRX files instead of the standard file list output but
still maintaining all the download features..

If we can achieve this we plan on make SEVERAL types of displays available and
the ability to omit unwanted areas. Of course all this will be incorporated
into ListIt if theres an interest.
@endnode

@node "16" "DIZLIST"
 DIZLIST is an include AREXX script which allows the BBS software to extract
the FILE_ID.DIZ description files that seems to have become standard. The
complete Docs to DIZLIST are in the file DIZ.CFG which should be placed in
your MEBBSNET:CONGFILES directory.
@endnode

